> > > how you were going to re-finish your bumpers,
> but powdercoating
> materials
> > > will not adhere to fiberglass or epoxy.
> > >
> > > Ed
> > > ----- Original Message -----
> > > From: Steve Bradley <scscomp(-at-)bellsouth.net>
