> > > > Grind down the bumper to bare metal. Fill the
> pits with fiberglass
> body
> > > > filler. After you sand the fiberglass filler
> smooth, I would put a
> > coating
> > > > of Epoxy primer (2 part, not the kind you buy
> at the FLAPS) and a coat
> > of
> > > > sandable primer. Sand the primer smooth and
> then apply the top coat.
